---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PHCDevworks"
  description="Design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure. Open source. Built for developers."
>
  <section style="margin-bottom: 12rem;">
    <h1
      style="font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 12rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 4rem; letter-spacing: -0.04em;"
    >
      PHCDEV<span style="color: #ff0055;">WORKS</span>
    </h1>
    <p
      style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 3rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
    >
      We build design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure.
    </p>
    <p
      style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem); line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.7;"
    >
      Everything is open source. Everything is on GitHub.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 12rem;">
    <h2
      style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 6rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em;"
    >
      PROJECTS
    </h2>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 5rem;">
      <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ff0055; padding-left: 2rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-tokens"
            style="color: #ff0055; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 4px solid #ff0055;"
          >
            SPECTRE TOKENS
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem); line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.8;"
        >
          Core design primitives for the Spectre suite. Colors, spacing,
          typography, radii, shadows. Outputs to CSS variables, JS/TS objects,
          and theme presets for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ff0055; padding-left: 2rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui"
            style="color: #ff0055; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 4px solid #ff0055;"
          >
            SPECTRE UI
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem); line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.8;"
        >
          Cross-platform UI built on Spectre Tokens. Tailwind-powered design
          system delivering consistent CSS utilities, component classes, and
          design recipes for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ff0055; padding-left: 2rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui-astro"
            style="color: #ff0055; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 4px solid #ff0055;"
          >
            SPECTRE UI ASTRO
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem); line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.8;"
        >
          First-class Astro layer for Spectre UI. Typed, SSR-friendly components
          (Button, Card, Input) that wrap Spectre UI classes and tokens. Native
          Astro, zero bloat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ff0055; padding-left: 2rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-icons"
            style="color: #ff0055; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 4px solid #ff0055;"
          >
            SPECTRE ICONS
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem); line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.8;"
        >
          Modern SVG icon sets for WordPress builders. Lucide, Font Awesome, and
          more. Unified manager, performance-first. Replaces dozens of separate
          icon plugins.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 12rem;">
    <h2
      style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 6rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em;"
    >
      PHILOSOPHY
    </h2>
    <div style="display: grid; gap: 4rem;">
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Design tokens once. <span style="color: #ff0055;">Use everywhere.</span>
      </p>
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Tokens feed CSS. <span style="color: #ff0055;"
          >CSS feeds components.</span
        >
      </p>
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        <span style="color: #ff0055;">Open source.</span> No vendor lock.
      </p>
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Build what you need. <span style="color: #ff0055;"
          >Modify what you want.</span
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 8rem;">
    <h2
      style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 3rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em;"
    >
      LINKS
    </h2>
    <p
      style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 2rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
    >
      <a
        href="https://github.com/phcdevworks"
        style="color: #ff0055; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 4px solid #ff0055;"
      >
        github.com/phcdevworks
      </a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem); opacity: 0.7;">
      All repos. All docs. All roadmaps.
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.5;">Â© 2025 PHCDevworks</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
